WEBVTT

00:00:11.617 --> 00:00:21.796 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
I close my eyes, and I can see
A world of peace, love, and harmony.

00:00:21.796 --> 00:00:26.927 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Come with me,
And you’ll see.

00:00:26.927 --> 00:00:29.555 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You will see.

00:00:33.894 --> 00:00:43.322 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
It’s not a dream, as I’m sure you know.
These things God promised so long ago

00:00:43.322 --> 00:00:48.745 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Are guaranteed,
Sure to be.

00:00:48.745 --> 00:00:51.164 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You will see.

00:00:55.461 --> 00:01:06.432 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Look around—
There’s joy and laughter in ev’ry sound.

00:01:06.432 --> 00:01:17.571 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Look and see—
This is the way our God meant it to be.

00:01:17.571 --> 00:01:27.416 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Those who fell asleep along the way,
They live again; we see them ev’ry day.

00:01:27.416 --> 00:01:32.630 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Come with me,
And you’ll see.

00:01:32.630 --> 00:01:34.925 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You will see.

00:02:03.917 --> 00:02:13.512 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
The pain and crying there used to be
Has gone forever; now it’s history.

00:02:13.512 --> 00:02:18.601 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Come with me,
And you’ll see.

00:02:18.601 --> 00:02:21.396 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You will see.

00:02:26.236 --> 00:02:36.498 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Look around—
There’s joy and laughter in ev’ry sound.

00:02:36.498 --> 00:02:47.594 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Look and see—
This is the way our God meant it to be.

00:02:47.594 --> 00:02:57.773 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Jehovah’s word is enough for me.
With eyes of faith, it’s reality.

00:02:57.773 --> 00:03:05.115 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
As we see
What’s in store,

00:03:05.115 --> 00:03:13.625 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You can be sure
Until the moon is no more,

00:03:13.625 --> 00:03:16.504 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
When you—

00:03:16.504 --> 00:03:26.515 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Close your eyes and come with me
To God’s world of peace and harmony.

00:03:26.515 --> 00:03:31.772 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
Come with me,
And you’ll see.

00:03:31.772 --> 00:03:36.903 line:90%,end position:50%,center align:center
You will see.

